\f0\i \cf0 Held:
\f1\i0 \'a0The judgment is affirmed. Pp.\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://supreme.justia.com/cases/federal/us/448/607/#630"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \strokec4 448 U. S. 630}}-662;\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://supreme.justia.com/cases/federal/us/448/607/#667"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \strokec4 448 U. S. 667}}-671;\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://supreme.justia.com/cases/federal/us/448/607/#672"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \strokec4 448 U. S. 672}}-688.\
