\cf0 MR. .JUSTICE STEVENS, joined by MR. CHIEF JUSTICE BURGER, MR. .JUSTICE STEWART, and MR. JUSTICE POWELL, concluded that the standard in question is invalid. Pp.\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://supreme.justia.com/cases/federal/us/448/607/#630"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \strokec4 448 U. S. 630}}-652,\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://supreme.justia.com/cases/federal/us/448/607/#658"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \strokec4 448 U. S. 658}}-659.\
