\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\i \cf0 Id.
\f1\i0 \'a0at 51-52. A NIOSH representative who testified later put it more succinctly, stating that, ". . . if benzene causes leukemia, and if leukemia is a cancer, then exposure really is almost moot."\'a0
\f0\i Id.
\f1\i0 \'a0at 1007.\
