\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 An amendment to the standard was promulgated on June 27, 1978. 43 Fed.Reg. 27962.\'a0
\f0\i See
\f1\i0 \'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://supreme.justia.com/cases/federal/us/448/607/#F22"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \strokec4 n}}\'a022,\'a0
