\f1\i0 \'a0n. 1,\'a0
\f0\i supra.
\f1\i0 \'a0However, even if it did, the Government's interpretation of the term "feasible," when coupled with its view of \'a7 3(8), would still allow the Agency to require the elimination of even insignificant risks at great cost, so long as an entire industry's viability would not be jeopardized.\
