\cf0 The Secretary concluded that, in light of the scientific uncertainty, he was not required to calculate benefits more precisely.\'a0
\f0\i Id.
\f1\i0 \'a0at 5941. In any event, he gave "careful consideration" to the question of whether the admittedly substantial costs were justified in light of the hazards of benzene exposure. He concluded that those costs were "necessary" in order to promote the purposes of the Act.\
