\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 The Secretary's decision was one, then, which the governing legislation authorized him to make. [{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://supreme.justia.com/cases/federal/us/448/607/#F4/35"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \strokec4 Footnote 4/35}}]\
